My first time ever writing a country song….the song is call “ Think too much “ and meaning behind this song is.

A man that does everything for everyone and rarely does he complain or stop doing what he does. He understands his role and him being a provider and all but that doesn’t mean he doesn’t get stressed out or go thru the motions of life… that usually happens when he thinks to much. Which also consists of drinking too much and breaking down at times( most of the time alone) Then after that he straightens back up and gets right back to what he’s supposed to do

If you ever lost somebody…. 😞🙏 🎶then you know how it feels….. 

Decided todo this cover after one of my friends passed away and this song always me think a lot about not wasting TIME! Wether it’s time spent on your self or spent with others. Pickup that call from ya parents whenever they call…. never leave ya people hanging whenever they call…

Hope you enjoyed my cover to “If I would’ve known” by Kyle Hume.

Shoutouts to my dawg @geeqpham1904 for helping me shoot this.
